<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Sample App</h1>
  <p>A Twitter clone app built <i>"from scratch"</i> with Ruby on Rails</p>
  <p>Source code of this app can be access at <a href="https://github.com/lethang7794/rails_sample_app">Github</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>
    Let's take a look at it
  </h2>

  <p>First, visit some user profile at Sample App:</p>
  <div>
    <ul>
      <%= link_to 'Barack Obama', '/BarackObama' %>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <%= link_to 'Newest user', user_path(@newest_user)  %>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <%= link_to 'Demo user', user_path(@demo_user) %>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>Next, create an account to try its awesome features.</p>

  <p>Just kidding. This is an awesome app. Just click the button below.</p>

  <div class="center">
    <%= form_with(url: '/login', model: @demo_user, scope: 'session', local: true, method: :post) do |f| %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :email %>
      <%= hidden_field_tag 'session[password]', 'password' %>
      <%= hidden_field_tag 'session[remember_me]', '1' %>
      <%= f.button class: "btn btn-rainbow" do %>
        <div class="flex flex-row flex-center">
          <div class="wrapper flex flex-row">
            <span class="text">Try this app</span>
            <span class="flex-center">
              <span class="margin-tran">
                <span class="my-arrow flex-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 16">
                    <path d="M12.58,0a1.19,1.19,0,0,0-1,.89,1.53,1.53,0,0,0,.29,1.42l3.71,4.53H1c-.63,0-1,.48-1,1.22a1.09,1.09,0,0,0,1.2,1.1H15.61l-3.73,4.52a1.52,1.52,0,0,0,0,1.91,1,1,0,0,0,1.63,0L19.18,9,20,8l-.82-.94L13.51.41A1,1,0,0,0,12.58,0Z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
